destroy.name: destroy
destroy.comment: Destroy webview, remove it from its parent

setJavascriptInterfaceScheme.name: setJavascriptInterfaceScheme
setJavascriptInterfaceScheme.comment:
Set javascript interface scheme.
-- see WebView::setOnJSCallback()

loadData.name: loadData
loadData.comment:
Sets the main page contents, MIME type, content encoding, and base URL.
-- param data The content for the main page.
-- param mimeType The MIME type of the data.
-- param encoding The encoding of the data.
-- param baseURL The base URL for the content.

loadHTMLString.name: loadHTMLString
loadHTMLString.comment:
Sets the main page content and base URL.
-- param string The content for the main page.
-- param baseURL The base URL for the content.

loadURL.name: loadURL
loadURL.comment:
Loads the given URL.
-- param url Content URL.

loadFile.name: loadFile
loadFile.comment:
Loads the given fileName.
-- param fileName Content fileName.

canGoBack.name: canGoBack
canGoBack.comment:
Gets whether this WebView has a back history item.
-- return WebView has a back history item.

canGoForward.name: canGoForward
canGoForward.comment:
Gets whether this WebView has a forward history item.
-- return WebView has a forward history item.

evaluateJS.name: evaluateJS
evaluateJS.comment: Evaluates JavaScript in the context of the currently displayed page.

setScalesPageToFit.name: setScalesPageToFit
setScalesPageToFit.comment: Set WebView should support zooming. The default value is false.

setOnShouldStartLoading.name: setOnShouldStartLoading
setOnShouldStartLoading.comment:
Call before a web view begins loading.
-- param callback The web view that is about to load new content.
-- return YES if the web view should begin loading content; otherwise, NO.

setOnDidFinishLoading.name: setOnDidFinishLoading
setOnDidFinishLoading.comment:
Call after a web view finishes loading.
-- param callback The web view that has finished loading.

setOnDidFailLoading.name: setOnDidFailLoading
setOnDidFailLoading.comment:
Call if a web view failed to load content.
-- param callback The web view that has failed loading.

setOnJSCallback.name: setOnJSCallback
setOnJSCallback.comment: This callback called when load URL that start with javascript interface scheme.

getOnShouldStartLoading.name: getOnShouldStartLoading
getOnShouldStartLoading.comment: Get the callback when WebView is about to start.

getOnDidFinishLoading.name: getOnDidFinishLoading
getOnDidFinishLoading.comment: Get the callback when WebView has finished loading.

getOnDidFailLoading.name: getOnDidFailLoading
getOnDidFailLoading.comment: Get the callback when WebView has failed loading.

setBounces.name: setBounces
setBounces.comment: Set whether the webview bounces at end of scroll of WebView.
